    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> sausages </strong>to a baking tray (or two!) with the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>,<strong> onion wedges </strong>and <strong>chopped pepper</strong></p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 25-30 min or until the sausages are cooked through (no pink meat!) and the potatoes are golden</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1669137509909-x200.jpg",
